BLE COMMUNICATION PROTOCOL
BLE Service Details
Parameter	Value
Device Name	"EXG"
Service UUID	12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789ABC
Characteristic UUID	ABCDEF12-3456-7890-1234-567890ABCDEF
Properties	NOTIFY
Descriptor	Client Characteristic Configuration (CCC) - 0x2902



2 Data Format
Transmission Type: Notifications (no confirmations required)

Data String Format:
<CH1>,<CH2>,<CH3>,<CH4>

Example:

324.5,298.2,75.3,82.1    // Note Here I generated Random Signal Values- For Real Time Value Need To connect EXG module

Value Ranges:

CH1 (EXG Signal): 0 - 409.5 (scaled from 12-bit ADC)

CH2 (Secondary EXG): 0 - 409.5

CH3 (Simulated): 50 - 100

CH4 (Simulated): 50 - 100


